text: Daniel Winkler (born 9 May 1959) is a Swiss rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Switzerland Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
